</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="4">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yang-tong-91" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yang-tong-91" class="zg-link" title="杨彤">杨彤</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-qi-63-64" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-qi-63-64" class="zg-link" title="王七">王七</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-ke-jian-43" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-ke-jian-43" class="zg-link" title="陈可鉴">陈可鉴</a></span>
